Global Automated DNA/RNA Extraction Market Insights
Automated DNA/RNA Extraction Market size was valued at USD 2.50 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.00 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Automated DNA/RNA Extraction Market Overview
The automated DNA/RNA extraction market is a rapidly growing sector driven by advancements in biotechnology and the increasing demand for accurate diagnostics, personalized medicine, and research applications. The market value in 2023 was estimated at $4.25 billion and is projected to reach $6.97 billion by 2030, with a CAGR of 7.1% during the forecast period. This growth is attributed to the increasing adoption of automated systems for the extraction process, which offer improved accuracy, efficiency, and scalability. The automation of DNA/RNA extraction is crucial in research laboratories, clinical settings, and the pharmaceutical industry.

